title: Ring of Fire - December 14 2013
description:
December 14, 2013
Ring of Fire 
Hosted by Robert F. Kennedy Jr., Mike Papantonio and Sam Seder


This week on Ring of Fire Radio:  Congressman Alan Grayson will tell us what House Democrats are doing to reign in Wall Street corruption.

Author Nomi Prins will explain why the Federal Reserve needs to concentrate on monetary policies that actually create jobs.

Joel Rubin from The Ploughshares Fund will tell us about the nuclear deal with Iran, and what it means for national security.

And author Chase Madar will join us for a discussion on the growing police state in America.
